@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Alternative One

autonumber

actor "Human Resources\nManager" as HRM
participant ":System" as System

activate HRM

    HRM -> System : asks to register a collaborator with a job \n and fundamental characteristics
    activate System

        System --> HRM : requests collaborator data (name, \n contact information, job position)
    deactivate System

    HRM -> System : inputs collaborator data
    activate System

        System --> HRM : shows a list of available job positions \n and asks to select one
    deactivate System

    HRM -> System : selects a job position
    activate System
        System --> HRM : presents a list of sectors of activity and \n asks to select one
    deactivate System

    HRM -> System : selects a sector of activity
    activate System

        System --> HRM : shows all data and requests confirmation
    deactivate System

    HRM -> System : confirms data
    activate System

        System --> HRM : displays operation success
    deactivate System

@enduml
